.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-LISTFUNDS" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-listfunds \- show on-chain and off-chain fund summary
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-listfunds
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns a summary of on-chain UTXOs and off-chain channel balances from
.BR listfunds .
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"onchain_sat":N, "offchain_msat":N, "offchain_sat":N, "utxo_count":N, "channel_count":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-onchain-balance (1),
.BR lightning-channel-local-balance (1)
